question: Which UNESCO World Heritage Site is located in Bulguksa, Gyeongju, South Korea?
asked_question_translated: Hvilket UNESCO-verdensarvssted ligger i Bulguksa, Gyeongju, Sydkorea?
answer: UNESCO-verdensarvsstedet i Bulguksa, Gyeongju, Sydkorea er Bulguksa-templet.
answer_translated_eng: The UNESCO World Heritage Site in Bulguksa, Gyeongju, South Korea is the Bulguksa Temple.
